Another great d/l ty. Do you have any other neil white books you can get hold of KK.
Many Thanks

Hi karaokeking, 

I have been looking for following books for quite sometime now but couldn't find them. Please help me if you can:

Down to a Sunless Sea – David Graham
The Last Gasp – Trevor Hoyle
Drowning Towers – George Turner
The Foundation Pit - Andrey Platonov
Nature's End - Whitley Strieber
A Gift Upon the Shore – M. K. Wren
Moscow – 2042 - Vladimir Voinovich
Skeletons on the Zahara: A True Story of Survival -  Dean King
The Slynx - Tatyana Tolstaya
The Cruel Sea - Nicholas Monsarrat
The Last Ship - William Brinkley
The Last Canadian - William C. Heine

Please note that some of the books were not originally written in english, but if you can find the translated version then it would be very much helpful.

Thanks.. :)

King, 
If you can help me with above request, then I would never trouble you again with any more requests. And even if they are not available, thanks for your tons of previous uploads.
